/* About */
"About Remodex" = "关于 Remodex";
"Control **Codex** from your iPhone." = "用你的 iPhone 控制 **Codex**。";
"The Codex runtime stays on your Mac. Your phone is a secure remote control connected through a relay." = "Codex 运行时始终留在你的 Mac 上。你的手机是一个通过中继连接的安全遥控器。";
"How It Works" = "工作原理";
"Your Mac runs a lightweight **bridge** that connects to a **relay server** over WebSocket." = "你的 Mac 会运行一个轻量级 **bridge**，通过 WebSocket 连接到 **relay server**。";
"You send a prompt from your phone" = "你从手机发出提示词";
"It travels through the relay to the bridge on your Mac" = "它会通过中继传送到你 Mac 上的 bridge";
"The bridge forwards it to `codex app-server` via JSON-RPC" = "bridge 会通过 JSON-RPC 将其转发给 `codex app-server`";
"Responses stream back the same path in real time" = "响应会沿相同路径实时流式返回";
"All execution happens locally on your Mac — code generation, tool use, file edits. Nothing runs on the relay." = "所有执行都在你的 Mac 本地完成，包括代码生成、工具调用和文件编辑。中继上不会运行任何内容。";
"Architecture" = "架构";
"Remodex iOS" = "Remodex iOS";
"Bridge (Mac)" = "Bridge（Mac）";
"WebSocket" = "WebSocket";
"JSON-RPC" = "JSON-RPC";
"JSONL rollout" = "JSONL 记录";
"The Relay" = "中继服务";
"A lightweight WebSocket server that routes messages between your iPhone and your Mac." = "一个轻量级 WebSocket 服务器，用于在你的 iPhone 和 Mac 之间转发消息。";
"Handles session discovery so your phone finds the Mac's live session" = "负责会话发现，让你的手机找到 Mac 上当前的活动会话";
"Never sees decrypted message contents after the handshake" = "握手完成后永远看不到解密后的消息内容";
"Only observes connection metadata — session IDs, device IDs, timing" = "只能看到连接元数据，例如会话 ID、设备 ID 和时间信息";
"You can **self-host** the relay on your own VPS, or use the default hosted endpoint from the npm package." = "你可以在自己的 VPS 上 **self-host** 中继，也可以使用 npm 包提供的默认托管端点。";
"Codex App-Server" = "Codex App-Server";
"The bridge spawns a **`codex app-server`** process — the same JSON-RPC interface behind the Codex desktop app and IDE extensions." = "bridge 会启动一个 **`codex app-server`** 进程，这也是 Codex 桌面应用和 IDE 扩展背后的同一套 JSON-RPC 接口。";
"Phone conversations are first-class Codex sessions" = "手机上的对话会被视为一等公民的 Codex 会话";
"Produces JSONL rollout files under `~/.codex/sessions/`" = "会在 `~/.codex/sessions/` 下生成 JSONL 记录文件";
"Threads started from your phone show up in Codex.app" = "从手机发起的线程会出现在 Codex.app 中";
"Already have a running Codex instance? Point the bridge at it with REMODEX_CODEX_ENDPOINT instead of spawning a new one." = "如果你已经有一个正在运行的 Codex 实例，可通过 REMODEX_CODEX_ENDPOINT 将 bridge 指向它，而不是重新启动一个新的实例。";
"Pairing & Security" = "配对与安全";
"On first connect, the bridge prints a **QR code** containing:" = "首次连接时，bridge 会输出一个包含以下信息的 **二维码**：";
"The relay URL" = "中继 URL";
"The session ID" = "会话 ID";
"The bridge's identity public key" = "bridge 的身份公钥";
"Scan it once from this app. After the handshake:" = "在此应用中扫描一次即可。握手完成后：";
"iPhone saves the Mac as a **trusted device** in Keychain" = "iPhone 会把这台 Mac 作为 **受信任设备** 保存到钥匙串中";
"Bridge persists your phone's identity locally" = "bridge 会在本地持久化保存你的手机身份";
"Later launches auto-reconnect — no QR needed" = "之后再次启动会自动重连，无需再次扫码";
"The QR remains available as a recovery path if trust changes or the session can't be resolved." = "如果信任关系发生变化或无法解析会话，二维码仍可作为恢复路径使用。";
"End-to-End Encryption" = "端到端加密";
"After pairing, every message is wrapped in encrypted envelopes:" = "配对完成后，每条消息都会被封装进加密信封：";
"Cipher" = "加密算法";
"AES-256-GCM" = "AES-256-GCM";
"Key derivation" = "密钥派生";
"HKDF-SHA256, per-direction keys" = "HKDF-SHA256，按方向分别派生密钥";
"Key exchange" = "密钥交换";
"X25519 ephemeral" = "X25519 临时密钥";
"Identity" = "身份认证";
"Ed25519 signatures" = "Ed25519 签名";
"Replay protection" = "重放保护";
"Monotonic counters" = "单调递增计数器";
"At-rest (iPhone)" = "静态存储（iPhone）";
"Keychain-backed AES key" = "由钥匙串保护的 AES 密钥";
"Git & Workspace" = "Git 与工作区";
"The bridge handles **git commands** from your phone locally on the Mac:" = "bridge 会在 Mac 本地处理来自手机的 **git commands**：";
"Also supports **workspace revert** — preview and apply reverse patches when the assistant makes changes you want to undo." = "还支持 **workspace revert**，可在助手做出你想撤销的更改时预览并应用反向补丁。";
"Connection Resilience" = "连接韧性";
"Auto-reconnect with exponential backoff (1s → 5s)" = "使用指数退避自动重连（1 秒 → 5 秒）";
"Bounded outbound buffer re-sends missed encrypted messages" = "受限的出站缓冲区会重新发送错过的加密消息";
"Codex process stays alive across transient drops" = "Codex 进程会在短暂断连期间保持存活";
"SIGINT / SIGTERM trigger clean shutdown" = "SIGINT / SIGTERM 会触发干净关闭";
"Desktop App Integration" = "桌面应用集成";
"Threads from your phone are persisted as JSONL rollout files, so they appear in **Codex.app** on your Mac." = "来自手机的线程会以 JSONL 记录文件的形式持久化，因此它们会出现在你 Mac 上的 **Codex.app** 中。";
"The desktop app doesn't live-reload external writes. Use the Hand off to Mac button in the app to continue the current thread on your Mac." = "桌面应用不会实时热加载外部写入。请使用应用中的 Hand off to Mac 按钮，在你的 Mac 上继续当前线程。";
"ISC License" = "ISC 许可证";

